            <h1 id="title">Tim Berners-Lee</title>
      
            <p id="alter-size">The man who created an alternative; gave those without voice's a way to speak, by creating HTML!</p>
            <div id="color-play">
            <figure id="img-div">
            <img id="image" src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.4503feefe33098cc708ae89b6a0edc61?rik=WR88O1WYizbrSQ&amp;pid=ImgRaw&amp;r=0" alt="Tim Berners-Lee, the man who created an alternative; gave those without voice's a way to speak, by creating HTML!">
            <figcaption id="img-caption">"The original idea of the web it should be a collaborative place where you can communicate through sharing information"</figcaption>
